            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>Fl</abbr><ex>avius</ex></expan> Felix <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>ir</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>larissimus</ex></expan> magister utriusque militiae <lb n="2"/>patricius et <expan><abbr>cons</abbr><ex>ul</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>ord</abbr><ex>inarius</ex></expan> et Padusia eius <expan><abbr>inl</abbr><ex>ustrissima</ex></expan> femina <lb n="3"/>voti co<expan><ex>m</ex><abbr>potes</abbr></expan> de proprio fecerunt
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Das Stück ist heute verschollen. Mosaik.</p>
